    <title type="html"><![CDATA[ComponentKit 最佳实践，注意细节]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.davidyanggo.me/blog/2015/04/02/componentkit-zui-jia-shi-jian-%2Czhu-yi-xi-jie/"/>
